Usage: SET NOTIFICATION_LEVEL [ALL|NONE|[-]<level> [-]<level> ...]
  The setting of this variable determines which types of
  events send desktop notifications. If ALL is specified,
  all supported event types will send desktop notifications.
  If NONE is specified, no desktop notifications will be
  sent.

  The <level> specification can be one of the following: 
    MSG            Private messages
    NOTICE         NOTICEs

  Example: when set to MSG, a desktop notification will be
  sent when a new private messages arrives.
